summary: this one can make your grass more denser and lost minimum FPS.
descriptionHtml:
english is not my mother language
amazing  dense grass is my personal mod which can make grass more dense.
this one can make your grass more denser and lost minimum FPS.
this one does not change the texture and mesh.so you can go with other grass mod.
if you are using SFO, this one should after it.
thie one does not contains only scripts,so it is very safe.

[size=4]setting:[/size]

in your skyrim.ini file
[Grass]
iMinGrassSize=80
if you want to more denser,you should set it at a lower number.
If you want a better performance,set it to 120 or more higher.
i just use iMinGrassSize=80
